# ðŸ”® The Archive of Forgotten Futures

A web-based interactive archive exploring **futures that could have been but never came to pass**.  
Visitors uncover branching timelines, salvaged fragments, and surreal hybrid worlds through an immersive, retro-futuristic interface.

