## Please note
This single HTML file uses Tailwind CSS for all styling and a simple JavaScript script to handle the dynamic content. 
When you click "Travel Beyond," it displays one of several pre-defined alternate futures, complete with a story and fragments. 
The "Salvage Fragments" and "Dream Generator" buttons will manipulate the content on the page, 
simulating the more complex features you requested.

The retro-futuristic aesthetic is created using a dark color scheme, a monospace font, glowing text, and terminal-like borders. 
The layout is fully responsive, adapting to different screen sizes.

